---
title: Cal Smart Tex-Mex Turkey Bowls with Mexican Street Corn Slaw
description: Lightly charred corn adds a lovely smoky quality to the Mexican- inspired slaw on top of a wild rice medley with Tex-Mex ground turkey and a cooling lime crema!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/bols-de-dinde-facon-tex-mex-60c9a525.jpg
